@startuml Admin Room Check-In Flow
title Admin Flow for Room Check-In
|Admin|
start
:Access Room Admin App;
:Logs in as Admin;
:Selects "Manage Events";
|System|
:Search for active events assigned to Admin;
:Returns list of active events;
|Admin|
:Selects event to manage;
|System|
:Loads event rooms and occupancy data;
:Returns room list with real-time occupancy;
|Admin|
:Selects "Room";
repeat
:Visualizes room details;
:Scan QR code from attendee ticket;
|System|
:Validates QR code;
:Authenticates attendee against event database;
if (Attendee has booking for this room?) then (No)
    if (Room at capacity?) then (Yes)
        note right
            Tickets are released on no-shows after a grace period;
        end note
        if (Spots to be released?) then (Yes)
            :Return spots available soon;
            |Admin|
            :Informs admin of upcoming spots;
            :Invites attendee to wait\n or try another session;
            detach
        else (No)
        |System|
        :Returns full capacity status;
        |Admin|
        :Informs admin of full capacity;;
        :Informs attendee to check \non the app for another session;
        endif

        detach
    else (No)
        |System|
        :Proceeds with check-in;
    endif
else (Yes)
endif
|System|
:Registers attendee check-in for session;
:Updates session occupancy data;
:Updates occupancy and inform clients;
:Returns success confirmation;
|Admin| 
:Show confirmation to admin;
:Admin let the attendee in;
backward :Repeat for next attendee;
@enduml